data.text:
The Oracle Corporation is an American multinational computer technology corporation headquartered in California.

History[]

Stark Expo[]

Larry Ellison, the CEO of Oracle Corporation, met Tony Stark while he was leaving the Stark Expo. Stark called him the "Oracle of Oracle". During the Battle at Stark Expo, Iron Man and War Machine defeated Whiplash in the Oracle Dome.[1]

Project P.E.G.A.S.U.S.[]

In conjunction with NASA and S.H.I.E.L.D., the Oracle Corperation supplied equipment to help study the Tesseract at the Joint Dark Energy Mission Facility in the Mojave Desert. The equipment supplied by the Oracle Corperation was destroyed along witht he facility during the Destruction of Project P.E.G.A.S.U.S..[2]

Mandarin Attacks[]

Investigating the attacks carried out by the Mandarin, Tony Stark had J.A.R.V.I.S. use the Oracle Corporation cloud database to plot all of the explosions above 3,000 degreese celsius located in the United States of America.[3]
